headline: Consumer Subscription Stocks Q4 Recap: Benchmarking Chegg (NYSE:CHGG)
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q4. Today, we are looking at consumer subscription stocks, starting with Chegg (NYSE:CHGG).
